Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}玲央
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}舞菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}玲央 你每天都這麼早來練習
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你的身體不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你才是 不是每天都陪我練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}覺得還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不過我懂你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不管上多少課 還是沒辦法有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你也是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}在之前那團時也是 一直想成為中央
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而一無反顧地上課 想比其他人多練習一些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:00:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的有絕對贏不了的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}「努力並不一定有回報」我很明自
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我只能努力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}怎麼會 玲央你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你們兩個好早喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}朝向狂歡節 最後衝刺吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}各位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}加油吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}能佔到看得清楚的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}比我想像的還早出場耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Maple 是壓軸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}畢竟壓軸是最受歡迎的團體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那不受歡迎的比較早出場嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不全然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}中間靠前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不上不下耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}(失落)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是工作人員入口耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是工作人員廁所耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}雖然我是偶像不會用 Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是工作人員走廊耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}外燴耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}在冒蒸氣耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那叫做 Hot Meal 喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好香喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}會被發現我們沒見過世面 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要走囉 兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好棒 有好多偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我們也是偶像喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Cham 的休息室在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Cham 好像在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好窄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這裡塞 七個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我有帶鍋子來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}又沒要吃烏龍麵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我可以去刷個牙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}等等 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}出去之後 右轉走到底有洗手台喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}為什麽你這麼清楚?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}對喔 玲央不是第一次來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}上次明明是壓軸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}抱歉 我沒有惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}玲央你很緊張嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這麼小的狂歡節就緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你這樣上不了武道館喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你真拼命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}繪里飄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因為我想好好享受舞菜的第一次狂歡節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我已經放棄以前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}接下來的初次體驗我絕對不會放過!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我再去買一張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}熊佐呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我刻意只買一張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}想把值得紀念的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好好地濃縮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be30}掉下去啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be30}我也知道會這樣 請壓抑一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我也只買一張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}下個的下個啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}總覺得開始緊張了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}ChamJam 要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}玲央
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}咦 要上場了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好早喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}會緊張嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}畢竟你很久沒上這麼大的舞台啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不過我覺得能和大家一起享受就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}也是 能好好享受就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我們 確定要上武道館了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}表演加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}玲央
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我要振作才行呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我是中央啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}各位抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你不用道歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我一直覺得玲央不該在 Cham
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我就是覺得你有這麼厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}從以前到現在 還有這個瞬間也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}優佳我最喜歡玲央央囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}雖然你可能不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不過在中央努力的你的背後出現很多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是出現什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我一直都這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}ChamJam 的中央是由好多好多愛組成的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}玲央
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}雖然你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}雖然你說過努力並不一定有回報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我覺得並不全然是白費
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}舞菜...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果100%中有1%得到回報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就把那1% 100%發揮在舞台上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我覺得你一定做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}各位 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我 能和 Cham 的各位來到這裡 好幸福...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我不要緊了 我不會停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}絕對不會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我們要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}一起去武道館
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}舞菜!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}舞菜~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}繪里飄小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}大家在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不只如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我能成為偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}能當偶像 真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我們是 ChamJam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}拜拜~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be30}真妃!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be30}夢莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}玲央!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\be30}舞菜!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}哎呀 雖然說好多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}請多說幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30\pos(620,1050)}Cham 的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30\pos(866,1050)}真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30\pos(984.5,1050)}非常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30\pos(1060.5,1050)}棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}居然能看到空音在那麼大的舞台跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}空音也很棒呢 雖然我沒在看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了 離 Cham 物販開始還有時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要做什麼殺時間呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}再吃一碗烏龍麵吧 慶祝烏龍麵!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}幹嘛說得像慶祝酒一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是在吵什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是 Maple 要開始表演了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}各位 等很久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我們是 Maple Doll
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}High 得好誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不愧是壓軸耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我們一起 High 到最後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我們也在同個舞台跳過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}超大成功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你們演唱會時有看到 Cham 的粉絲在哪裡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}看揮王劍的方式就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我們還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}確實向前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}重新梳化好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要發傳單囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}別浪費特典會開始前的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}宣傳到時間快完 要讓更多人記住 Cham!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}吉川先生好有幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好像社長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}現在不用說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}回答呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我們是 ChamJam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}晚點要開始物販
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那個 不介意的話請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}非常謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}繪里飄小姐在看 Maple 表演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}看哪個?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是想看哪個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}舞菜 你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}請給我一張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}請 不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}請來物販看看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}剛才那個挺可愛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要改推? 被發現我可不管喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be30}只有沒説就沒人知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}空音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這些人裡面有多少人是最喜歡舞台上的人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果被說最喜歡會很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}雖然會覺得原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不過去那個的人部落格一看 卻完全沒提到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我們明明只能相信他們所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}果然 還是希望是最喜歡我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要總是讓他們看見最可愛的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}只要讓他們覺得比以前更可愛 比以前更喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你就一直都是最喜歡的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的有很多偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}對啊 真的非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不過 在這麼多偶像裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}能遇見那一個玲央
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我覺得是我人生的寶藏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就算看了許多其他偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}也只能想起舞菜的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}明明有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的世界中只有舞菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不是第一名 是只有舞菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}基 今天表演如何呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯...我果然還是喜歡空音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}還有 我覺得幸好你是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果你不是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我一定說不出喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}謝謝你讓我說出喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}什 什麽! ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是第幾名喜歡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}當 當然是第一名啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我相信你喔 基
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}玲央 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我只看得見 Cham... 只看得見你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那當然 我從很久之前就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因爲有你在我才不緊張喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我有順利跳完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}舞菜隊伍有空喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be30}那邊的眼鏡 要不要排舞菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我先去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要說什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}舞菜 你今天也好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要說什麼...想在特別的這天說出特別的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那個 我能成為你的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}和哥哥 熊佐 繪里飄 經歷好多第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不過說你好努力了 好像又太跩...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的好開心 我覺得能遇到你太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}只有今天能說的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}說到只有今天能說的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不來排舞菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}沒人排就要結束囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我要排舞菜!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}呃...今天風和日麗...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}繪里飄小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你能站在最前排 我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你有好好享受到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那還用說嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我覺得非常開心也非常幸福!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}很努力的舞菜真的好可愛好棒!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}希望總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}能像今天和你一起去武道館就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不 不是希望 是一定會去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我必須為此更加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這是什麼生物 太可愛了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可愛到天上地下唯你獨尊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}難道是因為跨越了狂歡節這個大舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}也就是如果以後登上武道館或更高處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}舞菜到底有多無雙啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}繪里飄小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}多虧了你 我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726,1050)\be30}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(819,1050)\be30}有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1060.5,1050)\be30}有好好努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}非常謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}一輩子喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}武道館
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要是舞菜你登上武道館 我死而無憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要是舞菜你登上武道館
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我會死!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}終於來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:22:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這裡就是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}武道館
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好大! 武道館到底有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}原來那就是金色洋蔥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}狂歡節太 High 不小心乘著氣勢來到東京
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}有來真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}總有一天 Cham 要站在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}這裡是武道館...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}總覺得和想像的不同耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的沒錯嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是 是武道館啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我記得武道館上面不是有洋蔥嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}換個角度看也是洋蔥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}洋蔥切丁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}總有一天要登上這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要加油囉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be30}各位抱歉 果然好像不是這裡
